    (function () {

        'use strict';

        if (window.PerformanceObserver && performance && performance.mark && performance.getEntriesByName) {

            window.SRP = window.SRP || {};

            var paintObserver = new window.PerformanceObserver(function (list) {

                var paintEntries = list.getEntries();

                paintEntries.sort(function (a, b) {

                    return a.startTime - b.startTime;

                });

                // begin looking for TTI at first contentful paint

                if (!paintEntries || paintEntries.length < 2) {

                    // to avoid undefined issue on Safari

                    return;

                }

                var interactiveWindow = paintEntries[1].startTime;

                window.SRP.TTI_TIMER = { lastInteractiveWindow: interactiveWindow };

                var longTaskObserver = new window.PerformanceObserver(function (list) {

                    var longtaskEntries = list.getEntries();

                    for (var i = 0, len = longtaskEntries.length; i < len; i++) {

                        // if we find an idle window of >= 5000 ms, the beginning of that window was our timeToInteractive

                        if (longtaskEntries[i].startTime - interactiveWindow >= 5000) {

                            window.SRP.TTI_TIMER.timeToInteract = interactiveWindow;

                            longTaskObserver.disconnect();

                        }

                        interactiveWindow = longtaskEntries[i].startTime + longtaskEntries[i].duration;

                        window.SRP.TTI_TIMER.lastInteractiveWindow = interactiveWindow;

                    }

                });

                longTaskObserver.observe({ entryTypes: ['longtask'] });

                paintObserver.disconnect();

            });

            paintObserver.observe({ entryTypes: ['paint'] });

        }
